Too bad that this happens over and over again.<br>
<br>
Please: If your account got hacked, don't write <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>hundreds</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> of posts trying to prove that you are innocent. Change your passwords and shut up!<br>
